She graduated from the Gerasimov Institute of Cinematography in 1964.
She was awarded People's Artist of the USSR in 1988.
Her first husband was film director Evgeniy Vasilyev (Евгений Иванович Васильев), and they had one daughter.
Her second husband, writer Artur Makarov, was murdered in her apartment in 1995.
